{"type": "article", "id": 5661, "title": "Wafer 系列家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-29T08:06:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052338304Xy05IWkBDKxlnmA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本新兴家具品牌 MATSUSO T 日前邀请斯德哥尔摩设计师 Claesson Koivisto Rune 带来了全新「Wafer」系列的家具作品。深浅两色交错的木质条纹让 Wafer 系列中的这把椅子成为最大亮点，设计师将胡桃木与枫木结合，就像是糖果店里的华夫饼。两种木材的拼接为工艺提出了挑战，但最终成型的椅子看上去却丝毫未有拼接的痕迹，仿佛自然长出来的纹理一般，营造出图案化的条纹效果。日前，Wafer 系列已经在 2015 德国科隆国际家具展上展出，包括座椅、小型搁架以及小边桌。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233828M2udox9RvSNVfWc3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233829pMBgP4eqo25vZIHt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233829iY1SmxkMOnuNrfRy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233830Bk7KbDZPTLW2vH8G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}